<body>
<div>

<p source="SHANGBO.PENGZU 3.13.1 (STRIP 1) JI XUSHENG 3: 246">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-1a.1">狗老問于彭祖曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-1a.2">「狗氏執心不妄,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-1a.3">受命永長.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-1a.4">臣何藝可行,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-1a.5">能遷於朕身,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-1a.6">而謐于帝常?」</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.PENGZU 3.13.2 (STRIPS 1-3) JI XUSHENG 3: 246">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-2a.1">彭祖曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-2a.2">「休哉,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-2a.3">乃將多問因由,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-2a.4">乃不失度.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-2a.5">彼天之道,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-2a.6">唯恒 [...],</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-2a.7">不知所終.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.PENGZU 3.13.3 (STRIPS 3, 2) JI XUSHENG 3: 246">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-3a.1">狗老曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-3a.2">「眊眊余朕孳,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-3a.3">未則于天,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-3a.4">敢問為人?」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-3a.5">彭祖曰 [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-3a.6">言:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-3a.7">天地與人,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-3a.8">若經與緯,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-3a.9">若表與裏.」</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.PENGZU 3.13.4 (STRIP 2) JI XUSHENG 3: 246-247">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-4a.1">問:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-4a.2">「三去其二,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-4a.3">豈若已?」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-4a.4">彭祖曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-4a.5">「吁,汝孳孳薄問</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-4a.6">余告汝人倫, 曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-4a.7">戒之毋驕,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-4a.8">慎終保勞.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-4a.9">大圖之謱,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-4a.10">難易</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-4a.11">滯欲.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-4a.12">余〔告汝〕</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.PENGZU 3.13.5 (STRIP 5) JI XUSHENG 3: 247">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-5a.1">[...] 父子兄弟.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-5a.2">五紀畢周,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-5a.3">雖貧必修.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-5a.4">五紀不工,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-5a.5">雖富必失.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-5a.6">余告汝禍[...]</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.PENGZU 3.13.6 (STRIP 6) JI XUSHENG 3: 247">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-6a.1">[...]之謀不可行,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-6a.2">怵惕之心不可長,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-6a.3">遠慮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-6a.4">用素,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-6a.5">心白,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-6a.6">身釋.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-6a.7">余告汝咎.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.PENGZU 3.13.7 (STRIP 4) JI XUSHENG 3: 247">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-7a.1">[...] 既底於天,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-7a.2">又墜於淵,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-7a.3">夫子之德登矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-7a.4">何其崇.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-7a.5">故君之願良[...]</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.PENGZU 3.13.8 (STRIP 7) JI XUSHENG 3: 247">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-8a.1">[...]者不怡,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-8a.2">多務者多憂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-8a.3">賊者自賊也.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.PENGZU 3.13.9 (STRIP 7) JI XUSHENG 3: 247">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-9a.1">彭祖曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-9a.2">一命一修(?),</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-9a.3">是謂益愈.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-9a.4">一命三修,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-9a.5">是謂自厚.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-9a.6">三命四修,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-9a.7">是謂百姓之主.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.PENGZU 3.13.10 (STRIPS 7-8) JI XUSHENG 3: 247">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-10a.1">一命一(月+襄),</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-10a.2">是謂遭殃.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-10a.3">一命三(月+襄)</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-10a.4">是謂不長.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-10a.5">三命四(月+襄),</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-10a.6">是謂 絕輟.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-10a.7">毋逐富,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-10a.8">毋誇賢,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0043_tls_001-10a.9">毋尚樹.</seg>
                </p>

</div>
